data.title: Florence Nightingale | Nurse | Blue Plaques
data.meta_description: Blue Plaque commemorating reformer of the nursing organisation, nurse Florence Nightingale, at 10 South Street, Mayfair, London W1K 1DE, City of Westminster.
data.text:
Notes

This is a new plaque on rebuilt premises. The original plaque was erected by the Duke of Westminster in 1912 and removed when the house was pulled down in 1929.
